quran[40]{c,v,t}:
  19,59,Kodwa kwavela emva kwabo abalandeli (izizukulwana zamva) abaye abayinonophela iSalâh basuka balandela iinkanuko (zabo) ngenxa yoko ke baza kugagana nokungcola
  19,60,"Ngaphandle kwabo baguqukayo, bakholwe, benze izenzo zobulungisa; okwabo iya kuba kukungeniswa ePaladesi yaye abayi kwenziwa bugwenxa konke- konke"
  19,61,(Apho kukho) iMiyezo yokuhlala ngonaphakade leyo ingabonakaliyo uSozinceba Athembise ngayo izicaka zaKhe. Inene esaKhe isithembiso kunyanzelekile sizaliseke
  19,62,"Abayi kuva ntetho yakungcola apho ngaphandle (kombuliso) woxolo yaye baza kufumana isixhaso sabo apho, ekuseni nasemva kwemini"
  19,63,"Leyo ke yiPaladesi, eSiphisa ngayo njengelifa kwabo bazizicaka zeThu abaMoyikayo uAllâh"
  19,64,"(UJibrîl wathi): “Ke thina asihli (size emhlabeni) ngaphandle kwemvume yeNkosi yakho. OkwaYo koko kuphambi kwethu noko kungemva kwethu nokuphakathi apho. Ukanti iNkosi yakho Ayikhe Ilibale"
  19,65,INkosi yamazulu nomhlaba noko kungaphakathi kwawo Ke ngoko nqula Yona ube nomonde kunqulo lwaYo. Ingaba ikhona into oyaziyo efana naYo kusini na?”
  19,66,"Ke kaloku umntu (ongakholwayo) uthi, “Ndisakuba ndifile, ingaba ndiza kuphinda ndibuyiselwe ebomini?”"
  19,67,"Kanti umntu lo akakhumbuli na ukuba Samdala ngaphambili, lo gama wayengeyonto"
  19,68,"Ngoko (Ndifunga) ngeNkosi yakho, ngokuqinisekileyo Siya kubaqokelela nooSathana, Size sibenze babekhona bajikeleze isiHogo ngamadolo abo"
  19,69,Ke kaloku Siya kukhupha kwimvaba nganye abo yayingabona babengcole kakhulu ngokuchasene noSozinceba benendelelo
  19,70,Inene SiThi ababazi kakhulu abo bafanelwe kukutsha apho
  19,71,Yaye akukho namnye kuni (ongumenzi wobubi) ongazi kudlula kuwo (uMlilo)4 Oku kuxhomekeke eNkosini yakho yaye sele kumiselwe kungenakubuya kujike
  19,72,"Kekaloku SiyakubasindisaabobaMoyikayouAllâh, Sibayeke abenzi bobubi apho phakathi kuwo, beguqe ngamadolo"
  19,73,"Xa iivesi zeThu zicengcelezwa kubo njengobungqina obucacileyo, abo bangakholwayo, (basuke bathi): “Liliphi kula maqela (ethu) mabini elilelona linezinto (ubutyebi) nelilelona likhulu ngokwabalandeli"
  19,74,Kanti zingaphi izizukulwana eSazitshabalisayo ngaphambili kunabo ezazinezinto ngcono kunabo (nezazingcono kunabo) ngembonakalo
  19,75,"Yithi (Muhammad) Nabani na lowo uphambukileyo, uSozincebamakamolulele(ngokumandiselaubutyebinexesha lokuphila) bade bakubone oko babesoloko bethenjiswa ngako okungaba sisohlwayo okanye ibe yiYure, baza kwazi okokuba ngubani na okwimeko emaxongo, ingubani na ekungekho yakhe ngokwemikhosi"
  19,76,"Ke Yena uAllâh Wandisela isiKhokelo abo bahamba ngokulungileyo. Ke kaloku imisebenzi yobulungisa engaphelelwayo ingcono eNkosini yakho, ngokomvuzo yaye kungcono ukubhenela (kuYo)"
  19,77,"Umbonile na lowo ungakholwayo kwiiVesi zeThu, xa esithi, “Inene mna ndiya kunikwa ubutyebi nabantwana (kuBomi oBuzayo)?”"
  19,78,"Ingaba ebekhe wakroba kokungabonwayo na, okanye uthabathe isithembiso kuSozinceba"
  19,79,Nakanye! Siya kukubhala oko akuthethayo Size Simongezelele isohlwayo eside
  19,80,"Yaye Siya kumaba (okwelifa ukubhubha kwakhe) [uza kushiya] konke oko athetha ngako (ubutyebi nabantwana eSimnike bona kweli hlabathi), aze afike eyedwa (jwi) kuThi"
  19,81,Kananjalo bazithabathele (oothixo bobuxoki) ngaphandle koAllâh ukwenzela ukuba oko kubanike intlonipheko
  19,82,Nakanye! (abo thixo babo) baza kuluphika unqulo lwabo baze bachasane nabo (ngoMhla wokuGqibela)
  19,83,"Akuboni na ukuba Sithumele amaShayâtini (ooSathana) kwabangakholwayo, ababaphembelela ukwenza ukungcola ngempembelelo (eyenzeka rhoqo)"
  19,84,Ke wena musa ukungxama ngabo. Thina Sibabalela inani (elingephi leminyaka yokuphela kobomi babo kweli hlabathi)
  19,85,NgeMini esiya kuqokelela amalungisa kuSozinceba abe ligqiza
  19,86,Ke kaloku Siya kuqhubela abaphuli-mthetho esiHogweni benxaniwe (okweenkomo ezindilelwa emanzini ukuba ziye kusela)
  19,87,Akukho namnye oya kuba (namandla) akucenga ngaphandle kwalowo uthabathe umnqophiso kuSozinceba
  19,88,"Kananjalo bathi, “USozinceba Uthabathe (uzele) unyana.”"
  19,89,"Inene, nenze eyona nto imbi"
  19,90,"Amazulu anga angakrazuka, nomhlaba unga ungahlukana neentaba zidilike ziphasalake"
  19,91,Into yokuba babalele unyana kuSozinceba (uAllâh)
  19,92,Kodwa asinto ifanelekileyo kuSozinceba ukuba Abe nonyana
  19,93,Akukho namnye emazulwini nasemhlabeni ongazi kuSozinceba ukuba abe sisicaka (saKhe)
  19,94,"Inene (uAllâh) Wazi umntu ngamnye kubo, yaye Ubabalile ngobalo olupheleleyo"
  19,95,Yaye ngamnye kubo uya kuza kuYe (uAllâh ) eyedwa ngoMhla woVuko
  19,96,"Inene, abo bakholwayo benze izenzo zobulungisa, uSolubabalo Uya kubanika uthando"
  19,97,"Ke ngoko Thina Senze le (‘Kur’ân) yaba lula elwimini lwakho khon’ukuze unike iindaba ezivuyisayo kwabo bamoyikayo uAllâh, ulumkise kananjalo ngayo abachasi"
  19,98,Kanti zingaphi izizukulwana phambi kwabo eSazitshabalalisayo! Ingaba ungafumana nokuba mnye kuzo okanye uve nokuba kukusebeza kwabo (izizukulwana ezatshatyalaliswayo)